00:40:08.730 --> 00:40:11.830
these are people of
substantial economic power

00:40:11.830 --> 00:40:14.120
and substantial political power.

00:40:14.120 --> 00:40:16.020
So those kinds of
crimes and especially

00:40:16.020 --> 00:40:18.955
the land theft,
those are also crimes

00:40:18.955 --> 00:40:21.480
that have substantial
economic power behind them,

00:40:21.480 --> 00:40:24.090
so you are dealing with people
who are actually making money

00:40:24.090 --> 00:40:25.180
off the violence.

00:40:25.180 --> 00:40:28.310
There's not a lot of people
making money off malaria.

00:40:28.310 --> 00:40:30.790
There's not a lot of
