00:46:08.280 --> 00:46:09.830
Have you given or
are there others

00:46:09.830 --> 00:46:13.510
doing similar lines of research?

00:46:13.510 --> 00:46:16.450
GARY HAUGEN: Yeah,
and that is the case

00:46:16.450 --> 00:46:19.610
and as I said the
first half of my career

00:46:19.610 --> 00:46:21.507
was addressing those
failures actually

00:46:21.507 --> 00:46:22.590
here in the United States.

00:46:22.590 --> 00:46:24.923
So there's no abuse taking
place overseas that I haven't

00:46:24.923 --> 00:46:27.660
seen somewhere here
in the United States.

00:46:27.660 --> 00:46:30.530
What we do have is just
